	<Install>
		<Step><![CDATA[
			<p>Download and extract the plugin.</p>
		]]></Step>
		<Step><![CDATA[
			<p>It is recommended that you backup your ZenCart first.</p>
		]]></Step>
		<Step><![CDATA[
			<p>Upload the <code>includes</code> folder from the extracted plugin to your ZenCart
				webshop's root directory.</p>
		]]></Step>
		<Step><![CDATA[
			<p>Go to <code>Modules &rarr; Shipping</code>. The module you are looking for is suffixed
				by "(Bring Fraktguide)".</p>
		]]></Step>
		<Step><![CDATA[
			<p>Install the shipping options you want by clicking the "Install" button next to them.</p>
		]]></Step>
	</Install>
